== Look's Absolute Return Fund ==
Look's Absolute Return Fund 為公司旗艦基金。<ref name="wenwei">{{cite news |url=http://paper.wenweipo.com/2016/09/03/FI1609030009.htm |title=陸東許沂光開證券公司 |language=中文 |work=[[文匯報_(香港)|文匯報 (香港)]] |date=2016-09-03 |accessdate=2017-04-05 }}</ref>
